title: WHAT UP GUYS?
body: My name is GUY FERRARI! I am looking to make a trip to FLAVORTOWN. But this covid-19 virus has caused me to lose my sense of taste. Now I'm big sad :(

title: Can someone bust me out of jail?
body: I've got tiger cubs, meth, whatever you want. Also, need someone to help me deal with that woman in Tampa...you know who.

title: Anyone looking for their dog?'
body: I found a small dog near the WRAL soccer fields. Please email me your name and a photo/description of your missing dog and I will let you know if she\'s a match. email: joel@email.com
